data.description: Gorgeous Views on a 1/4 acre greenbelt lot with a 3 car garage!  Meticulously maintained, spacious, open floor plan with 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths and enclosed loft.  Enjoy your own oasis in the master bedroom, that's large enough for a private sitting area & complete with a vaulted ceiling.  Secondary bedroom and full bath on first floor.  Located in the NEISD school district & highly sought after Johnson High School.  Come see this rare gem today!
data.whatILove: This house has been a joy to live in!  The view has been one of the best parts about living here; we feel like we have had our own little oasis!  The neighborhood has been wonderful.  The people are all so friendly and the neighbors are great!  We are very excited for the family that decides to call this house their home; it is truly a gem!
